{"name":"Fury of the Saddle","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Starting at 7th level, you can use your dragon as a mount if your size is medium or smaller. While you are riding your dragon, it cannot fly. </p><p>Additionally, if your dragon moves 20 feet straight towards a target and hits them with a bite attack on the same turn, the target takes an extra 1d6 piercing damage. If the target is a creature it must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be frightened until the end of its next turn. </p><p>The DC is equal to 8 + your dragon’s Charisma modifier + your Proficiency bonus.</p><p><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\" /></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Rider 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/creatures/reptiles/serpent-horned-green.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.custom-dragon-knight-class.hH6y5uHJdgQIvUjW"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674504664638,"modifiedTime":1674860798413,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"1BJ9EEmqI2M6a1fv"}
{"name":"Frightful Presence","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 7th level, your dragon companion unnerves enemies that approach too close. Whenever an enemy creature begins their turn within 20 feet of your companion, they must make a Wisdom saving throw, or be frightened of your dragon companion until the start of their next turn. If they succeed, they are immune to your Frightful Presence for 24 hours.</p><p><strong>Frightful Presence save DC</strong> = 8 + your proficiency bonus + your dragon's Charisma modifier</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":"Enemy begins their turn within 20 feet"},"duration":{"value":"","units":"spec"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"8 + @prof + @ability.cha.mod","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Companion 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/fear-fright-mask-orange.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.custom-dragon-knight-class.6l1LSRV9NoyncWXX"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674771307649,"modifiedTime":1674859697473,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"47jeZmzXC365c3lr"}
{"name":"Companion's Bond","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 1st level, your dragon gains a number of benefits because of the bond you have forged together.</p><p>In combat the dragon acts during your turn, and obeys your commands. It can move and use its reaction on its own, but the only action it takes is the Dodge action, unless you take a bonus action on your turn to command it to take another action. That action may be one in its stat block or some other action. If you are incapacitated, your dragon acts on its own and will attempt to bring you to safety. If you're absent, it rolls its own initiative.</p><p>Your dragon can't take the Attack action, be used as a mount, or fly with a creature it has grappled.</p><p>Your dragon companion’s proficiency bonus is equal to your own. While not wearing barding, your dragon companion has a natural armor class of 14 + its proficiency bonus.</p><p>For each dragon knight level after 1st, your dragon companion gains hit points equal to 6 + its Constitution modifier, and it gains one additional hit die. The dragon's hit dice are d10s, regardless of its size. When the dragon is reduced to 0 hit points, it makes death saving throws as a player would.</p><p>Your dragon companion also gains proficiency in two skills of your choice, and shares your saving throw proficiencies.</p><p>While on the same plane, you and your dragon always know the direction to one another, and can communicate with vague images, emotions, and feelings, regardless of distance to one another.</p><p>Whenever you gain the Ability Score Improvement class feature, your dragon's abilities also improve. Your dragon can increase one ability score of your choice by 2, or it can increase two ability scores of your choice by 1. As normal, your dragon can't increase an ability score above 20 using this feature. Your dragon companion can't take feats.</p><p>Your dragon shares your alignment, and has a personality trait and a flaw that you can roll for or select from the tables below. Your dragon shares your ideal, and its bond is always \"I will protect my knight; I will do the best I can for my knight; I will die for my knight.\"</p><table class=\"w-100 rd__table  stripe-odd-table\"><thead><tr><th class=\"col-1\" data-rd-isroller=\"true\">[[/r d4]]</th><th class=\"col-11\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Trait</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"col-1\" data-roll-min=\"1\" data-roll-max=\"1\">1</td><td class=\"col-11\">I love to collect gems and art pieces.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1\" data-roll-min=\"2\" data-roll-max=\"2\">2</td><td class=\"col-11\">If you threaten my friends, you threaten me.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1\" data-roll-min=\"3\" data-roll-max=\"3\">3</td><td class=\"col-11\">I stay on alert so others can rest.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1\" data-roll-min=\"4\" data-roll-max=\"4\">4</td><td class=\"col-11\">I love to explore, so that I can discover and learn about different cultures.</td></tr></tbody></table><table class=\"w-100 rd__table  stripe-odd-table\"><thead><tr><th class=\"col-1\" data-rd-isroller=\"true\">[[/r d4]]</th><th class=\"col-11\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Flaw</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"col-1\" data-roll-min=\"1\" data-roll-max=\"1\">1</td><td class=\"col-11\">As a dragon, I'm naturally superior to others.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1\" data-roll-min=\"2\" data-roll-max=\"2\">2</td><td class=\"col-11\">I'm secretly terrified of other dragons.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1\" data-roll-min=\"3\" data-roll-max=\"3\">3</td><td class=\"col-11\">I hold permanent grudge against anyone who offends my knight.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1\" data-roll-min=\"4\" data-roll-max=\"4\">4</td><td class=\"col-11\">I get jealous when my knight spends time with people other than me.</td></tr></tbody></table></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Knight 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"chained-heart.svg","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.8LAXliVKMEhidHGZ"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674458194788,"modifiedTime":1674851372776,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"4t1txfRegAROGCSI"}
{"name":"Paralysis Breath","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-1182ccb8-7fff-da10-ec0d-236d3a6ac110\">Each creature in the area must succeed on a @ability.con.mod saving throw or be @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.rules.w7eitkpD7QQTB6j0.JournalEntryPage.xnSV5hLJIMaTABXP]{paralyzed} for 1 minute, a creature can repeat the saving throw  at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success.</strong></span></p><p><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\" /></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"1","units":"minute"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"cone"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"@abilities.con.mod","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"With a grin, @actor exhales a sparkling silver gas that races towards those in its path","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Companion 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/air/fog-gas-smoke-dense-gray.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.NNgdaFcL8J4DC3fe"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674520161919,"modifiedTime":1674798938582,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"5hlFY3SUPLWuUXTi"}
{"name":"Eye for Detail","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-8a5ee350-7fff-3e04-d340-d3e795f66488\">At 3rd level, you can easily discern the value and rarity of gems, art pieces, and magical items. You can spend 1 minute studying a gem or art piece, after which you learn its exact value. Additionally, if it is a gemstone, you learn what kind of gemstone it is. If it's an art piece, you learn how old it is. </strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-8a5ee350-7fff-3e04-d340-d3e795f66488\">    Furthermore, you can cast the @spell[identify]</strong><em><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-8a5ee350-7fff-3e04-d340-d3e795f66488\"> </strong></em><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-8a5ee350-7fff-3e04-d340-d3e795f66488\">spell, but only as a ritual. You don't require material components for the spell when you cast it this way.</strong></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Knight 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/perception/eye-ringed-green.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.custom-dragon-knight-class.siSCG7GqPBb1UHvU"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674459535545,"modifiedTime":1674798915916,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"6JXrGXLPcv3T3bVL"}
{"name":"Titanic Roar","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-61a84b00-7fff-7c1a-ac9a-21751214c633\">Your can let loose a vicious roar, filling nearby creatures with dread. </strong></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.249498701095581;margin-right:0.912353515625pt;margin-top:1.125396728515625pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-61a84b00-7fff-7c1a-ac9a-21751214c633\">    As an action on your turn, you can roar. Any number of creatures of your choice within 60 feet of you must make a Wisdom saving throw against your breath weapon DC. On a failed save, creatures are frightened of you for 1 minute. The creature can repeat the saving throw at the end each of their turns, ending the effect on a success. Once you have used this ability, you can not do so again until you finish a long rest.</strong></span></p><p><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\" /></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":"inst"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":60,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"Kael releases a terrible roar, frightening enough to cause lesser creatures to flee in terror","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"con"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Companion 13","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/fear-fright-monster-purple-blue.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.custom-dragon-knight-class.Q3MpnY4FJp3LO1XV"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674528400685,"modifiedTime":1674859760074,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"6mgMwOthulY9QIwd"}
{"name":"Rending Fang","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-48fd7018-7fff-cce3-cf99-3e0fd3249370\">The damage of your dragon companion's bite attack increases to 2d6.</strong></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2494932651519775;margin-left:0.0809326171875pt;margin-right:16.142120361328125pt;text-indent:9.001434326171875pt;margin-top:1.1253662109375pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-48fd7018-7fff-cce3-cf99-3e0fd3249370\">Additionally, your dragon companion's attacks count as magical for the purpose of overcoming resistance and immunity to non-magical attacks and damage</strong></span></p><p><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\" /></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Companion 5","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/creatures/abilities/fangs-teeth-bite.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.custom-dragon-knight-class.cBpguUVZtuZUCOT1"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674519246645,"modifiedTime":1674852992980,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"8Cy3V8CLHKMoV3sw"}
