{"name":"Rider","type":"subclass","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f7bd1807-7fff-881a-fa7b-c2cd26252898\">The bond between a dragon knight and their dragon is strong, but those of the Rider Practice take that even further. They seek to live and to die beside their dragon, a sentiment shared by the dragon itself. While not all riders mount their dragons, those who don't are rare. Those of the Rider Practice fight in tandem with their dragon, and win in tandem with them.</strong></span></p><p>You gain a number of features at select levels in this Practice:</p><p>Level 3: @UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.DOnUvkJpfLHYOhdl]{Coordinated Strikes}, @UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.bTwn8LKZ2jKi8QJI]{Draconic Instinct}, @UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.lEPKC417LmxnkzJ6]{Riders Bond}</p><p>Level 7: @UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.1BJ9EEmqI2M6a1fv]{Fury of the Saddle}</p><p>Level 10: @UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.S5rZHDwcDOM8is9l]{Sky Rider}</p><p>Level 15: @UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.LwWGBM2XOQpO7cyP]{Dragon's Fang}</p><p>Level 18: @UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.DXNurmSHmKODVbtQ]{Cascading Roar}</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","identifier":"rider","classIdentifier":"dragon-knight","advancement":[{"type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.DOnUvkJpfLHYOhdl","Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.bTwn8LKZ2jKi8QJI","Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.lEPKC417LmxnkzJ6"],"optional":false,"spell":{"ability":"","preparation":"","uses":{"max":"","per":""}}},"value":{},"level":3,"title":"Features","icon":"systems/dnd5e/icons/svg/item-grant.svg","_id":"IqKhxhfrIJlKNLPG"},{"t