{"name":"Path of the Sun Warrior","type":"subclass","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>The Sun Warriors are the people of an ancient civilization who first discovered the ability to manifest solar energy from their inner rage. Most keep their power a secret, as it is the most sacred power a barbarian could possess. Taught how to control their rage, like the sun controls its inner heat; these barbarians from time to time can unleash their merciless wrath, like the sun scorches with primal devastation. Peoples of many faiths and background honor this power, some believing that this same power was gifted to mortals along with the creation of the sun.</p><p>As you walk along the Path of the Sun Warrior you are granted a number of features as your level increases.</p><p>3rd Level: </p><p>6th Level:</p><p>10th Level:</p><p>14th Level:</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"HB: PotSW","identifier":"path-of-the-sun-warrior","classIdentifier":"barbarian","advancement":[{"_id":"EpWjxHw4j6JsHz8D","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.henZyYZp8cFQExYq","Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.MYlEsnYN6zY4m7pF"],"optional":false,"spell":{"ability":"","preparation":"","uses":{"max":"","per":""}}},"value":{},"level":3,"title":"Features"},{"_id":"G5iReUC76EacW7hw","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.axGPIeRQu3PMjcV2"],"optional":false,"spell":{"ability":"","preparation":"","uses":{"max":"","per":""}}},"value":{},"level":6,"title":"Features"},{"_id":"FEuljJ3IaffPOwK8","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.MZS8sJsDQkujlog0"],"optional":false,"spell":{"ability":"","preparation":"","uses":{"max":"","per":""}}},"value":{},"level":10,"title":"Features"},{"_id":"sq8sjUuB9ekU9YtJ","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.n0yhK