{"name":"Draconic Breath","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 6th level, you have learned how to create a larger blast of elemental chaos.  The type and damage of this exhalation is determined by your color. </p><div><table><tbody><tr><td><p>Dragon</p></td><td><p>Breath Type</p></td><td><p>Area of Effect</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Black</p></td><td><p>Acid</p></td><td><p>5 by 60 ft. line (Dex save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Blue</p></td><td><p>Lightning</p></td><td><p>5 by 60 ft. line (Dex save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Brass</p></td><td><p>Fire</p></td><td><p>30 ft. cone (Dex save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Bronze</p></td><td><p>Lightning</p></td><td><p>5 by 60 ft. line (Dex save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Copper</p></td><td><p>Acid</p></td><td><p>5 by 60 ft. line (Dex save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Gold</p></td><td><p>Fire</p></td><td><p>30 ft. cone (Dex save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Green</p></td><td><p>Poison</p></td><td><p>30 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Red</p></td><td><p>Fire</p></td><td><p>30 ft. cone (Dex save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Silver</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.wLYHEh8AIvTBXqd1]{Cold}</p></td><td><p>30 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>White</p></td><td><p>Cold</p></td><td><p>30 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>As a bonus action on your knights turn, you may be commanded to exhale a breath weapon. Each creature in the area takes a number of d8s of damage equal to your proficiency bonus on a failed save, and half as much damage on a successful save. </p><p><strong>Breath save DC</strong> = 8 + your Constitution modifier + your Proficiency bonus </p><p>   You may use this breath weapon in conjunction with your @UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.ThtqDBY3bK0xS6TN]{Debilitating Breath} a number of times equal to your Constitution modifier. At 10th level the range of this breath weapon doubles.</p><p><br /></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"action","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":"inst"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"@actor exhales a blast of frigid air and ice onto their enemies","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["@scale.dragon-companion.elemental-breath","cold"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"con"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Companion 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/creatures/abilities/dragon-fire-breath-orange.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.gVlXVrVfOFvgIWFw"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674515998574,"modifiedTime":1674858815582,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"FO6JTZx5msKc8gQI"}
{"name":"Claw","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You makes a melee weapon attack against a creature within 5 feet of you. On a hit, the target takes 1d6 slashing damage, and an extra 1d6 damage, and you may attempt to grapple the target. This extra damage increases to 2d6 at 13th level. The additional damage is the same type as the one associated with your Draconic Covenant. </p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":"inst"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":5,"long":5,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"Kael swipes with his razor sharp claws.","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","slashing"],["@scale.dragon-companion.claw-cov","cold"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Companion 9","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/creatures/claws/claw-talons-glowing-orange.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.custom-dragon-knight-class.lQycoisa9Gd1Mbzv"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674525575721,"modifiedTime":1674857008617,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"GDs10vac6qdVNFOi"}
