{"name":"Greater Draconic Breath","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 6th level, you have learned how to create a larger blast of elemental chaos. The type and damage of this exhalation is determined by your color. </p><div><table><tbody><tr><td><p>Dragon</p></td><td><p>Breath Type</p></td><td><p>Area of Effect</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Black</p></td><td><p>Acid</p></td><td><p>5 by 30 ft. line (Dex save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Blue</p></td><td><p>Lightning</p></td><td><p>5 by 30 ft. line (Dex save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Brass</p></td><td><p>Fire</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Dex save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Bronze</p></td><td><p>Lightning</p></td><td><p>5 by 30 ft. line (Dex save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Copper</p></td><td><p>Acid</p></td><td><p>5 by 30 ft. line (Dex save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Gold</p></td><td><p>Fire</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Dex save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Green</p></td><td><p>Poison</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Red</p></td><td><p>Fire</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Dex save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Silver</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.rdBFdv5saC1AsZvp]{Cold}</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>White</p></td><td><p>Cold</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>As a bonus action on your knights turn, you may be commanded to exhale a breath weapon. Each creature in the area takes a number of d8s of damage equal to your proficiency bonus on a failed save, and half as much damage on a successful save. </p><p><strong>Breath save DC</strong> = 8 + your Constitution modifier +  your Proficiency bonus.</p><p>   You may use this breath weapon in conjunction with your enervating breath a number of times equal to your Constitution modifier.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":"inst"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"@actor exhales a blast of frigid air and ice onto their enemies","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["@scale.dragon-companion.elemental-breath","cold"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"con"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Companion 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/creatures/abilities/dragon-fire-breath-orange.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.gVlXVrVfOFvgIWFw"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674515998574,"modifiedTime":1674859533045,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"GY11yc0EerNZjRKZ"}
{"name":"Draconic Growth","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 9th level, you have grown and matured further, allowing you to fight together with your Knight more fluidly. You gains the following features:</p><ul><li><p>Your size is now large, you can support your Knight as a mount while flying, and are able to fly with a creature you has grappled. Your bite attack damage die are increased to d8s and you have a reach of 10 feet. Additionally, you increases your speed by 10 feet and your flying speed by 20 ft.     </p></li><li><p>You gain advantage on all saving throws so long as you can see your Knight. </p></li><li><p>You gains a number of attack options that you may take in place of your bite attack. You are proficient with these, and adds your Strength modifier to their attack and damage rolls. If an attack causes a creature to make a saving throw, the save DC is equal to 8 + your proficiency bonus + the your Strength modifier.</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.GDs10vac6qdVNFOi]{Claw}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.QtRuPJQASMd8icSv]{Tail}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.nO1bKGhg00DK0KNL]{Wing Gust}</p></li></ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Companion 9","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/creatures/reptiles/dragon-winged-blue.webp","effects":[],"flags"