{"name":"Dragon's Fang","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f2ad2154-7fff-8cdb-aca8-a036a0521709\"> At 15th level, you and your dragon are able to tear through your enemies. If your dragon moves at least 20 feet straight toward a creature and then hits it with a melee weapon attack in the same turn, the target takes an extra 2d6 damage. </strong></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.249497127532959;margin-right:0.2764892578125pt;margin-top:1.1246337890625pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f2ad2154-7fff-8cdb-aca8-a036a0521709\">    Additionally, your dragon can use an action to rampage and make a claw attack against any number of creatures within 5 feet of it, with a separate attack roll for each target. If you're within 5 feet of your dragon when they rampage, you can use your reaction to make a melee weapon attack against each creature within your reach that was attacked by your dragon during their rampage. Your dragon can't rampage again until you finish a short or long rest.</strong></span></p><p><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\" /></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Rider 15, Dragon Companion 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/commodities/bones/bone-jaw-teeth-white.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.custom-dragon-knight-class.aCIEEp8CGv9wiWNv"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674504995743,"modifiedTime":1674859065898,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"LwWGBM2XOQpO7cyP"}
{"name":"Solar's Wrath","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, solar energy begins to emerge from you when you enter rage, growing more intense as your inner rage increases.</p><p>Whenever you enter your rage you gain 1 Heat Point. The maximum number of Heat Points you can maintain while raging is 2 + your Proficiency bonus + your additional Rage Damage. You gain 1 Heat Point whenever you it a creature with a weapon attack, and 2 if the attack is a critical. All of your Heat Points disappear whenever your rage ends.</p><p>You gain the following benefits while you have Heat Points:</p><ul><li><p>All your weapon attacks deal extra fire or radiant damage (your choice) equal to the number of Heat Points you have.</p></li><li><p>Whenever you are hit by an attack, you may use your reaction to release radiant flames from you. Each creature within 10 feet of you takes fire or radiant damage equal to the number of Heat Points you have.</p></li></ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"HB: PotSW","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Path of the Sun Warrior 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/light/explosion-star-glow-orange.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.custom-sun-barbarian-path.QHW1IYBjINI0CLkl"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674532165492,"modifiedTime":1674862489543,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"MYlEsnYN6zY4m7pF"}
{"name":"Radiant Light","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>The light you can produce with @UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.henZyYZp8cFQExYq]{Illuminating Sun} becomes more lasting and empowers your abilities when someone is exposed to its radiance. The light you emit with Illuminating Sun counts as magical, and if any of this light overlaps with an area of darkness created by a spell 3rd level or lower, that @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.S7VbUetIfVT7B6Eq]{Darkness} is dispelled.</p><p>Additionally, you may force any creature you hit with a weapon attack that is within the bright light from @UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.henZyYZp8cFQExYq]{Illuminating Sun} to make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, that target becomes @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.rules.w7eitkpD7QQTB6j0.JournalEntryPage.0b8N4FymGGfbZGpJ]{blinded} until the end of your next turn.</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses once you finish a long rest.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"HB: PotSW","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Path of the Sun Warrior 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/light/explosion-star-large-orange.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.custom-sun-barbarian-path.z3L19w5UmJxvYpm5"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674535392191,"modifiedTime":1674862406333,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"MZS8sJsDQkujlog0"}
{"name":"Greater Debilitating Breath","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You has developed the ability to adjust your breath weapon to debilitate other creatures. This second breath weapon’s effects are determined by your color . </p><div><table><tbody><tr><td><p>Dragon</p></td><td><p>Breath Type</p></td><td><p>Area of Effect</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Black</p></td><td><p>Paralysis</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Blue</p></td><td><p>Repulsion</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Str save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Brass</p></td><td><p>Sleep</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Bronze</p></td><td><p>Repulsion</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Str save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Copper</p></td><td><p>Slowness</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Gold</p></td><td><p>Weakness</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Str save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Green</p></td><td><p>Sleep</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Platinum</p></td><td><p>Paralysis</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Red</p></td><td><p>Weakness</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Str save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Shadow</p></td><td><p>Weakness</p></td><td><p>15 ft cone (Str save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Silver</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.tOAp43Gdb2yA9pKk]{Paralysis}</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>White</p></td><td><p>Slowness</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>Your dragon may use this type of breath weapon in place of its elemental breath weapon. Your dragon may use all its breath weapons a combined number of times equal to its Constitution modifier, and regains all uses when it completes a short or long rest.</p><p><strong>Breath save DC</strong> = 8 + your proficiency bonus + your dragon's Constitution modifier </p><p>The details of these breath weapons can be found at the end of this class. Additionally, the range of this breath weapon doubles at 10th and again at 14th level</p><p><br /></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":"inst"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"@abilities.con.mod","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Companion 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/air/fog-gas-smoke-dense-white.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.dX5JypqQzvzynV4H"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674519425779,"modifiedTime":1674859343395,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"MuDMAMdYe9uNi3xd"}
{"name":"Draconic Covenant","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 1st level, you form a covenant with a type of dragon. The damage type associated with each dragon is used by features you gain later. You also gain the service of a dragon, who's statistics can be found at the end of the document. The dragon gains additional damage immunities and traits, depending on the type of dragon you chose for your Draconic Covenant.</p><table class=\"w-100 rd__table  stripe-odd-table\"><caption>Dragon Covenant</caption><thead><tr><th class=\"col-3 text-center\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Dragon</th><th class=\"col-2\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Damage Type</th><th class=\"col-3 text-center\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Dragon</th><th class=\"col-9\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Damage Type</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">Black</td><td class=\"col-2\">Acid</td><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">Gold</td><td class=\"col-9\">Fire</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">Blue</td><td class=\"col-2\">Lightning</td><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">Green</td><td class=\"col-9\">Poison</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">Brass</td><td class=\"col-2\">Fire</td><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">Red</td><td class=\"col-9\">Fire</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">Bronze</td><td class=\"col-2\">Lightning</td><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">Silver</td><td class=\"col-9\">Cold</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">Copper</td><td class=\"col-2\">Acid</td><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">White</td><td class=\"col-9\">Cold</td></tr></tbody></table><p>When you die, your dragon also dies after a number of hours equal to your dragon knight level. If your dragon companion is ever slain, the magical bond you share allows you to return it to life. With 8 hours of work and the expenditure of 25 gp worth of precious gems per your dragon knight level, you can call forth your companion's spirit and use your magic to create a new body for it. You can return a dragon companion to life in this manner even if you do not possess any part of its body.</p><p>Returning your dragon to life is a grueling process, and you must expend a number of hit dice equal to half your dragon knight level (rounded up) to perform this ritual.</p><p>Finally, you can speak, read, and write Draconic due to the bond you and your dragon share.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Knight 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"dragon-spiral.svg","effects":[{"label":"Draconic Covenant","icon":"dragon-spiral.svg","changes":[{"key":"system.traits.languages.value","mode":0,"value":"aarakocra","priority":20}],"transfer":false,"_id":"WFjDzxZZvpUh3xn3","disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"origin":null,"tint":null,"flags":{"dae":{"selfTarget":false,"selfTargetAlways":true,"stackable":"none","durationExpression":"","specialDuration":[]},"core":{"statusId":""}}}],"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.MeD4FlJSQzzz4WvP"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674456503895,"modifiedTime":1674851402946,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"O7wa5Sf5FaVJ1eS7"}
{"name":"Tail","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You make a melee weapon attack against a creature within 10 feet of you. On a hit, the target takes 1d10 bludgeoning damage, and must succeed on a Strength saving throw or be knocked prone. The reach of this attack increases to 15 ft at 17th level, and its damage increases to 2d10.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":"inst"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":10,"long":10,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"Kael whips his tail towards the creature, attempting to knock it to the ground.","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["@scale.dragon-companion.tail","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"str","dc":null,"scaling":"str"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Companion 9","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/creatures/abilities/tail-swipe-green.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.custom-dragon-knight-class.JFeS4zO1nYiiUQej"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674526179587,"modifiedTime":1674856989315,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"QtRuPJQASMd8icSv"}
