{"name":"Sky Rider","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-bbf74f28-7fff-bdf0-52db-77526406096c\">At 10th level, you and your dragon rule the sky. Mounting and dismounting your dragon only costs 5 feet  of movement instead of half your speed, you have  advantage on saving throws made to avoid falling off your dragon, and neither you or your dragon take fall damage if you fall 20 feet or less. </strong></span></p><p><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\" /></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Rider 10, Dragon Companion 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/creatures/abilities/wing-batlike-white-blue.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.custom-dragon-knight-class.7iZB9ZzZIjjKlpWy"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674504807212,"modifiedTime":1674852320870,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"S5rZHDwcDOM8is9l"}
{"name":"Dragon's Heart","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You and your dragon bolster each other's resolve in the face of terrible foes. You and your companion gain advantage to saving throws against being frightened whenever you and your dragon can see each other.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Knight 5, Dragon Companion 5","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/life/heart-red-blue.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.5md5lFyXScMaKJFg"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674861017046,"modifiedTime":1674861255816,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"SfKG6jdFg6o1JIHh"}
{"name":"Debilitating Breath","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>This second breath weapon’s effects are determined by your color. </p><div><table><tbody><tr><td><p>Dragon</p></td><td><p>Breath Type</p></td><td><p>Area of Effect</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Black</p></td><td><p>Paralysis</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Blue</p></td><td><p>Repulsion</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Str save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Brass</p></td><td><p>Sleep</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Bronze</p></td><td><p>Repulsion</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Str save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Copper</p></td><td><p>Slowness</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Gold</p></td><td><p>Weakness</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Str save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Green</p></td><td><p>Sleep</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Platinum</p></td><td><p>Paralysis</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Red</p></td><td><p>Weakness</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Str save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Shadow</p></td><td><p>Weakness</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Str save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Silver</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.5hlFY3SUPLWuUXTi]{Paralysis}</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>White</p></td><td><p>Slowness</p></td><td><p>15 ft. cone (Con save)</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>Your dragon may use this type of breath weapon in place of its @UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.FO6JTZx5msKc8gQI]{Draconic Breath}. Your dragon may use all its breath weapons a combined number of times equal to its Constitution modifier, and regains all uses when it completes a short or long rest.</p><p>Breath save DC = 8 + your Constitution modifier + your Proficiency bonus </p><p>    The details of these breath weapons can be found at the end of this class. Additionally, the range of this breath we