{"name":"Dragon's Fury","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-c036533a-7fff-16fa-a621-c8018725e2f1\">You may take the Multiattack action in place of your attack action. You may make three attacks; one bite and two claw attacks.</strong></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Companion 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/creatures/claws/claw-talons-yellow-red.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.custom-dragon-knight-class.wWm3oXjC2Sfysnfb"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674528939402,"modifiedTime":1674798910002,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"mtRGTISIL408hgT7"}
{"name":"Sun's Avatar","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You gain resistance to fire and radiant damage.</p><p>Additionally, you enter a state of explosive heat when you reach the maximum value of heat points, granting you the following benefits until your rage ends:</p><ul><li><p>Your reach with your melee weapon attacks increases by 5 feet.</p></li><li><p>Your weapon attacks deal fire of radiant damage (your choice) instead of its normal damage type.</p></li><li><p>You may use your @UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.MYlEsnYN6zY4m7pF]{Solar's Wrath} feature as a bonus action in addition to its normal activation.</p></li><li><p>The range of your @UUID[Compendium.dragon-knight-and-sun-warrior.module-items.MYlEsnYN6zY4m7pF]{Solar's Wrath} feature increases to 20 feet, and you may choose which creatures to affect.</p></li></ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"HB: PotSW","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Path of the Sun Warrior 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/light/explosion-beam-impact-silhouette.webp","effects":[{"label":"Sun's Avatar","icon":"icons/magic/light/explosion-beam-impact-silhouette.webp","changes":[{"key":"system.traits.dr.value","mode":0,"value":"fire","priority":20},{"key":"system.traits.dr.value","mode":0,"value":"radiant","priority":20}],"transfer":false,"_id":"QQIdMHoMuJpR2VNz","disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"comb