{"name":"Wing Gust","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Rather than making an attack, you may beat its wings. Medium or smaller creatures of your choice within 15 feet of you must make a Strength saving throw. On a failed save, a creature is pushed 10 feet away from the dragon. The range of the push and distance a creature is pushed on a failed save increases by 5 feet at 13th level, and 10 feet at 17th level. Immediately after making this special attack, you can move up to half your flying speed. </p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":"inst"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":15,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"cone"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"Kael beats his wings with the force of a gale.","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"str","dc":null,"scaling":"str"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Companion 9","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/commodities/biological/wing-green.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.custom-dragon-knight-class.DAkBdLokJ99UZSvI"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674526570596,"modifiedTime":1674857035466,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"nO1bKGhg00DK0KNL"}
{"name":"Fulfilled Covenant","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-09cc60c7-7fff-3f9d-0c25-2cdaf207f494\">You and your dragon share hit points, the total of which is equal to your hit point maximum + your dragon’s hit point maximum. Whenever one of you takes damage, that damage is subtracted from your combined hit point maximum. When this hit point maximum hits 0, both you and your dragon fall unconscious, but only you make death saving throws. If you become stable or die, so does your dragon. If you receive any healing, both you and your dragon return to consciousness. When you spend hit dice during a short rest, you can use both your hit dice and your dragon’s hit dice to restore hit points.</strong></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Knight 20, Dragon Companion 20","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/control/buff-flight-wings-runes-blue-white.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.custom-dragon-knight-class.TOobQSYLHZmFO3bc"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674513908160,"modifiedTime":1674859499574,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"q7KjuMNbrW0RQCrh"}
{"name":"Arctic Breath","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You exhale a 60 foot cold of cold. This cold deals a number of d8's equal to your proficiency modifier on a failed Constitution saving throw, and half as much on a save.</p><p></p><p>The breath save DC is equal to 8 + Constitution modifier + your Proficiency bonus</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":"inst"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":60,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"cone"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"@abilities.con.mod","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"con","actionType":"other","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"@actor exhales a blizzard-like blast of subzero air and ice shards upon those who stand before him","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["@scale.dragon-comapnion.elemental-breath","cold"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"con"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Companion 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/creatures/abilities/dragon-ice-breath-blue.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.gVlXVrVfOFvgIWFw"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674515998574,"modifiedTime":1674856455729,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"rdBFdv5saC1AsZvp"}
{"name":"Ability Score Improvement (Dragon Knight)","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you reach 4th level, and again at 6th, 8th, 12th, 16th, and 19th level, you can increase one ability score of your choice by 2, or you can increase two ability scores of your choice by 1. As normal, you can't increase an ability score above 20 using this feature.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Knight 4, Dragon Companion 4","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.sPy2OLoN7JaAcMl4"}},"img":"icons/skills/melee/weapons-crossed-swords-yellow.webp","effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1661787234431,"modifiedTime":1674851858941,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"rpXWGTvtOXiwp9X7"}
{"name":"Incapcitating Breath","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-1182ccb8-7fff-da10-ec0d-236d3a6ac110\">Each creature in the area must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or be @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.rules.w7eitkpD7QQTB6j0.JournalEntryPage.xnSV5hLJIMaTABXP]{paralyzed} for 1 minute, a creature can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success.</strong></span></p><p><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\" /></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DK","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"1","units":"minute"},"cover":null,"target":{"value":60,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"cone"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"@abilities.con.mod","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"con","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"With a grin, Kael exhales a silver gas, filled with flecks of blue and gold, that races towards those in its path","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"con"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Dragon Companion 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/air/fog-gas-smoke-dense-gray.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.NNgdaFcL8J4DC3fe"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674520161919,"modifiedTime":1674859296894,"lastModifiedBy":"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU"},"ownership":{"default":0,"IFGv1j1vWaUhnrGU":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"tOAp43Gdb2yA9pKk"}
